    "# load important dependencies \n",
    "import optimtool as oo\n",
    "from optimtool.base import np, sp, plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "tags": []

   "source": [
    "# 无约束优化（optimtool.unconstrain）\n",
    "```python\n",
    "import optimtool.unconstrain as ou\n",
    "ou.[方法名].[函数名]([目标函数], [参数表], [初始迭代点])\n",
    "```\n",
    "$$\n",
    "f(x)=\\sum_{i=1}^{n/2}(-13+x_{2i-1}+((5-x_{2i})x_{2i}-2)x_{2i})^2+(-29+x_{2i-1}+((x_{2i}+1)x_{2i}-14)x_{2i})^2, x_0=[0.5, -2, 0.5, -2, ..., 0.5, -2].\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import optimtool.unconstrain as ou\n",
    "x = sp.symbols(\"x1:5\")\n",
    "f = (-13 + x[0] + ((5 - x[1])*x[1] - 2)*x[1])**2 + \\\n",
    "    (-29 + x[0] + ((x[1] + 1)*x[1] - 14)*x[1])**2 + \\\n",
    "    (-13 + x[2] + ((5 - x[3])*x[3] - 2)*x[3])**2 + \\\n",
    "    (-29 + x[2] + ((x[3] + 1)*x[3] - 14)*x[3])**2\n",
    "x_0 = (1, -1, 1, -1) # Random given"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 梯度下降法（gradient_descent）\n",

    "| steepest(funcs: FuncArray, args: ArgArray, x_0: PointArray, verbose: bool=False, draw: bool=True, output_f: bool=False, method: str=\"wolfe\", epsilon: float=1e-10, k: int=0) -> OutputType                                           | 使用线搜索方法求解非精确步长（默认使用wolfe线搜索）         |\n",

    "## 信赖域方法（trust_region）\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "ou.trust_region.[函数名]([目标函数], [参数表], [初始迭代点])\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
